{"tid":499013,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"( 三國 ) 除呂布 邊個最好揪？","createTime":"2017-12-14T10:50:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-16T14:36:56.000Z","uid":2719,"like":38,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":95,"replies":[{"pid":"6de001f0da5e649f2923e4e221731922b0cd710c","tid":499013,"uid":2719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T10:50:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">個人覺得係許褚</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">巨人身體 如姚明打曾志偉﹕</span><br />\n「長八尺余，腰大十圍，容貌雄毅，勇力絕人」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">力大無窮 成年人打小朋友﹕</span><br />\n「許褚單手倒拖牛尾走了百步，賊寇大驚，不敢要牛就走了。」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">馬超都淆 一人嚇疾全場﹕</span><br />\n「曹操與馬超、韓遂等單馬會語，只帶了許褚前往。馬超本來想乘此機會襲擊曹操本人......許褚怒目瞪視馬超，於是馬超不敢實施行動」<br />\n<br />\n大家又覺得邊個最好揪呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"324df287edb68b5748a6ecc01c546be41f02f904","tid":499013,"uid":7452,"like":5,"dislike":64,"score":-59,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T10:54:54.000Z","msg":"邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e49a1131a993df946e5ebd7928422b7ecf25b0e","tid":499013,"uid":16061,"like":74,"dislike":1,"score":73,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T10:54:58.000Z","msg":"關羽唔係搞掂佢咩?"},{"pid":"53474196c47e582bd9c6ba30b50d5ba1fdee1287","tid":499013,"uid":2889,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T10:55:00.000Z","msg":"趙雲"},{"pid":"a2c6ff54b2059c2c86db8c34424fd913b8849831","tid":499013,"uid":102096,"like":48,"dislike":0,"score":48,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T10:57:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7969c469cc11bee9bf91266a392012d26d0b7372","tid":499013,"uid":60115,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T10:57:55.000Z","msg":"潘無雙"},{"pid":"18f6c56f28b2dc07ba6298037861e2179739804c","tid":499013,"uid":119290,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T11:00:16.000Z","msg":"孫策，有名你叫小霸王"},{"pid":"bc6e77fb711551594ba30111e176eda6d2fb6928",